text: Dechi Marcel N'Guessan (born 12 November 1991) is an Ivorian footballer who plays as a midfielder for Malaysia Premier League club Terengganu II. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Ivorian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Malaysia Premier League players Category:UiTM FC players
